text: int main ( ) { int n1 , n2 , i , gcd , lcm ; int T ; scanf ( "%d" , & T ) ; while ( T -- ) { scanf ( "%d %d" , & n1 , & n2 ) ; for ( i = 1 ; i <= n1 && i <= n2 ; i ++ ) { if ( n1 % i == 0 && n2 % i == 0 ) { gcd = i ; } } lcm = ( n1 * n2 ) / gcd ; printf ( "%d %d" , gcd , lcm ) ; } return 0 ; }
